text: Liquiçá is one of the municipalities (formerly districts) of East Timor. Its capital is also named Liquiçá. ==Administrative posts== The municipality's administrative posts (formerly sub-districts) are: *Bazartete *Maubara *Liquiçá The administrative posts are divided into 23 sucos ("villages") in total. Category:Municipalities of East Timor
title: Liquiçá Municipality
